- Compile the mpihelloworld program:

# mpiCC mpihelloworld.c -o mpihelloworld 

- PBS script is in: mpihelloworld.pbs 
Use mpirun with "--allow-run-as-root" only if necessary - it is not generally recommended.

- Submit to the queue (normally, under a non-root user):

# sbatch mpihelloworld.pbs 

- See more info about SLURM and its commands in slurm_commands.txt and slurm_vs_torque.txt
